readme:
Service Usage

This services notifies when an alert against a person of interest or a document has been matched at the border.

Service Flow

  1. AMS sends an AMSNotificationRequest.xsd message to the ESB
  2. The ESB transforms the AMSNotificationRequest.xsd message into a SV625 message
  3. The transformed message is then sent onto subscribers

Transformation

AMS Provider messages are transformed on the ESB into SV625 enterprise messages. When routing the SV625 message to AGD a further filter transformation is run which drops information AGD is not interested in.
